REMOTE DOWNLOAD NOT AVAILABLE - please contact data@library.columbia.edu for access. Tibet 1 Square Kilometer Grid With 2000 Population Census Data is a polygon theme representing 1 square kilometer areas in Tibet Province China. Tibet 1 m Grid With 2000 Population Census Data

This data layer is part of the Tibet 2000 Township Census data set produced by the All China Marketing Research Co. and distributed by the University of Michigan, China Data Center.
